HEADWORD: Mummiform
<hw>Mum"mi*form</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[<ets>Mummy</ets>
+ <ets>-form</ets>.]</ety> <def>Having some resemblance to a mummy; --
